<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Head-of-GIS-laboratory" title="Head of GIS laboratory " alt="link">Head of GIS laboratory </a></h2>

	
					<p>The International Maize and Wheat Improvement Center (CIMMYT) invites applications for the position of Head of GIS laboratory within the Socio-economics Program. The position will be based at the CIMMYT’s headquarters 45 Km. northeast of Mexico City, but the selected candidate will be expected to travel on a regular basis to Asia and Africa. The initial appointment is three years, subject to the continued disbursement of approved funds, after which further employment is subject to performance. Deadline: 31 March 2009</p>
