						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Young-people-urged-to-do-their-part-to-ensure-food-security" title="Young people urged to do their part to ensure food security" alt="link">Young people urged to do their part to ensure food security</a></h2>

	
					<p>Jamaica’s youth are being encouraged to plant backyard gardens to ensure reliable food supply as the global crisis worsens. Detective Corporal Dane Brown of the May Pen police, told the youngsters they were not too young to be a part of the initiative to ensure food security. He informed the students that an insufficient food supply would negatively affect the total population, leading to various problems, which would ultimately affect the country's development. (Source: Jamaica Information Service, 16 March 2009)</p>
							<p><span class="date">24/03/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
